---
import Container from "../../primitives/Container.astro";
---
<section class="section-pad bg-white" aria-labelledby="our-story-title">
  <Container>
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16 lg:items-start">

      <!-- Left: Story text -->
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Our Story</p>
        <h2 id="our-story-title" class="fluid-h2 mt-3">
          A clear mission.<br />Delivered at scale.
        </h2>
        <p class="fluid-lead mt-6 text-muted">
          Empereal was founded in 2008 in Singapore with a simple but ambitious belief: sustainable energy and water infrastructure should be technically excellent, architecturally elegant, and economically viable — simultaneously.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-5 text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Over the past 18 years we have grown from a focused solar engineering practice into a trusted global EPC partner with deep expertise in Solar PV, Architectural BIPV Façades, Solar Thermal Desalination, Energy Storage, and Green Hydrogen.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Mission + Vision cards -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 reveal">
        <!-- Mission -->
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-primary-dark p-7 ring-1 ring-accent/20">
          <div class="absolute -top-8 -right-8 h-32 w-32 rounded-full bg-accent/10 blur-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-9 w-9 rounded-lg bg-accent/20 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" class="h-4 w-4 text-accent" fill="none">
                <path d="M10 2a8 8 0 100 16A8 8 0 0010 2zm0 3a1 1 0 011 1v4l2.5 2.5a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L9.5 11.414A1 1 0 019 10.5V6a1 1 0 011-1z" fill="currentColor"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-accent tracking-wide uppercase text-sm">Mission</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
            To deliver integrated clean energy and water solutions that perform for decades, respect the environment, and create lasting value for the communities and clients we serve.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Vision -->
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-surface border border-primary/10 p-7 ring-1 ring-primary/10">
          <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -left-8 h-32 w-32 rounded-full bg-accent/8 blur-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-9 w-9 rounded-lg bg-accent/15 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" class="h-4 w-4 text-accent-dark" fill="none">
                <path d="M10 3.5a6.5 6.5 0 100 13 6.5 6.5 0 000-13zM2 10a8 8 0 1116 0A8 8 0 012 10zm8-3a1 1 0 011 1v2.586l1.707 1.707a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414l-2-2A1 1 0 019 11V8a1 1 0 011-1z" fill="currentColor"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-primary-dark tracking-wide uppercase text-sm">Vision</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-ink leading-relaxed">
            A world where every building generates power, every community has clean water, and every industry runs on renewable energy — decentralized, decarbonized, and democratized.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
